# Avatar — React

Package: `@acko/avatar`
Directive: none (presentational)

## Props Interface

```typescript
interface AvatarProps {
  src?: string;
  alt?: string;
  initials?: string;
  size?: 'xs' | 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' | 'xl';
  shape?: 'circle' | 'square';
  className?: string;
}
```

## Fallback Hierarchy

1. `src` → renders `<img>` with `object-fit: cover`
2. `initials` → renders text with primary-subtle background
3. Neither → renders fallback User icon (lucide-react)

## Exports

```typescript
export { Avatar } from './Avatar';
export type { AvatarProps } from './Avatar';
```
